    "body": "![medium](https://www.gstatic.com/codereviewagent/medium-priority.svg)\n\nInstead of using PostgreSQL-specific `pg.UUID`, use the dialect-agnostic `Uuid` type introduced in SQLAlchemy 2.0. This ensures compatibility with other databases like SQLite (which is used in your test suite) without needing dialect-specific workarounds.\n\n```suggestion\nfrom sqlalchemy import String, Uuid\n```",
