    "body": "![medium](https://www.gstatic.com/codereviewagent/medium-priority.svg)\n\nIn SQLAlchemy 2.0, it is highly recommended to fully type-annotate relationships using `Mapped` for better type safety and editor autocompletion.\n\n```suggestion\n    devices: Mapped[list[\"Device\"]] = relationship(\n        \"Device\", back_populates=\"customer\", cascade=\"all, delete-orphan\"\n    )\n    subscriptions: Mapped[list[\"SubscriptionService\"]] = relationship(\n        \"SubscriptionService\", back_populates=\"customer\", cascade=\"all, delete-orphan\"\n    )\n```",
